attributes.attrExprVal:
CASE 
WHEN SRC_DIM_ORDER_LINE_STATUS.ORDER_LINE_STATUS_CODE   IS NULL THEN 'INS'
WHEN SRC_DIM_ORDER_LINE_STATUS.meta_row_hash_type2   <> SRC_STG_DIM_ORDER_LINE_STATUS.meta_row_hash_type2   THEN 'TY2'
WHEN SRC_DIM_ORDER_LINE_STATUS.meta_row_hash_type1   <> SRC_STG_DIM_ORDER_LINE_STATUS.meta_row_hash_type1   THEN 'TY1'
END
CASE WHEN JNR_dim_order_line_status.operation_ind = 'INS' THEN to_timestamp_ntz('1900-01-01 00:00:00') ELSE JNR_dim_order_line_status.meta_timestamp END
di_cf(row_number() over(partition by SRC_STATUSCODE.STATUSCODE ,SRC_STATUSCODE.LABEL order by SRC_STATUSCODE.STATUSCODE ,SRC_STATUSCODE.LABEL))
